Capi version 0.03
=================

This is still very incomplete.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Time::HiRes

  libc20.a from the AVM CAPI ADK (available from ftp://ftp.avm.de)
    It has to be placed in subfolder c20lib.

  Of course CAPI itself has to be installed, including header files


